                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">* Describes mobile and wireless design techniques from the developer's perspective, offering in-depth analysis of the complete range of network technologies<br>    * Details development options for building Smart Client, Thin Client, and messaging applications as well as PIM (personal information management) and location-based services<br>    * The author is an experienced trainer who leads seminars and workshops worldwide for iAnywhere Solutions, a subsidiary of Sybase</span>
              
