                    <span>As a developer I got a little dissapointed. A lot of words, but very little substance that I could use directly. I think the word 'Design' is somewhat misleading and also the subtitle 'A developer's approach to developing innovative mobile and wireless solutions'. The book is just an 'overview' for beginners.</span>
                  
